時間がないんです！彼、本当に妊娠してるんです！
We don't have time! He's really pregnant!

717
00:42:12,564 --> 00:42:17,364
破水したんです！病院に行かないと！
His water just broke! Oh my god! We have to go to the hospital!

718
00:42:17,364 --> 00:42:22,064
今すぐ病院に行かないといけないんです、お願いします！
And we have to go to the hospital right now, please!

719
00:42:22,064 --> 00:42:27,064
嘘をついているように見えます。嘘じゃありません！
I think they're liars. We are not... We're not lying!

720
00:42:27,064 --> 00:42:31,864
ほら、こんなにお腹が大きいんです！妊娠していないと思います。
Look how big he is! I think she's not pregnant, sir.

721
00:42:31,864 --> 00:42:37,064
すみません、夫は本当に妊娠してて、今すごくお腹が大きいんです！
Excuse me, my husband is really pregnant! He's really big right now.

722
00:42:37,064 --> 00:42:40,064
赤ちゃんに触らせて。
Let me feel the baby.

723
00:42:40,064 --> 00:42:46,564
蹴ってる！ほら、感じない？私の息子！
It's kicking! It's kicking! Can you not feel it? My son!

724
00:42:46,564 --> 00:42:49,864
あなたの跡継ぎよ！静かに！
Your heir! Silenzio!

725
00:42:49,864 --> 00:42:57,564
どう思う？あの二人、ちょっと怪しい行動をしてるよね。
What do you think? Those two, those two are acting a little bit suspicious.

726
00:42:57,564 --> 00:43:03,564
マンマ・ミーア！大丈夫？
Mamma mia! Are you alright? Do you think... Could it be?

727
00:43:03,564 --> 00:43:12,064
そう、ほら！まさに私が思っていた通りだわ！
Yes, see! This is exactly what I was thinking!

728
00:43:12,064 --> 00:43:20,564
私の息子！私が妊娠しているから引き止めるのね！
My son! No, no, no, you are stopping us because I am pregnant! Yes! It was the baby!

729
00:43:20,564 --> 00:43:27,864
そこに馬がいた。いいえ、私の赤ちゃんです！
There was a horse there. No, it was my baby! It was our baby!

730
00:43:27,864 --> 00:43:34,064
トランクからひづめの音が聞こえたんだけど。
Recently, I heard a hoof sound coming from the truck. Hey! You can't say that about my baby!

731
00:43:34,064 --> 00:43:41,064
ちょっと見せてもらってもいいかしら？嫌です！
Mind if we take a look? I do mind! I do mind! Wait, wait, wait!

732
00:43:41,064 --> 00:43:45,064
ダメダメダメ！トランクの中を見るわよ。
No, no, no, no! We're just going to take a look in the trunk.

733
00:43:45,064 --> 00:43:52,064
お願い、やめて！あなたは間違いなく有罪よ！
Please! No, please! You are definitely guilty!

734
00:43:52,064 --> 00:43:55,864
お願い、警察官さん！やめてください！
Please, officer! Stop, officer, please!

735
00:43:55,864 --> 00:44:00,564
馬だ、警部！馬よ！
It's a horse, officer! A horse!

736
00:44:00,564 --> 00:44:05,064
馬だ！私の息子よ！
It's a horse! It's my son! It's ours!

737
00:44:05,064 --> 00:44:13,064
ジジ・ムリン、セシリア・イマーグリーン、あなたたちを逮捕するわ。
Gigi Murin, Cecilia Immergreen, you're under arrest.

738
00:44:13,064 --> 00:44:21,064
逮捕なんて嫌だ！失うものが多すぎる！
I can't be under arrest! I have too much to lose!

739
00:44:21,064 --> 00:44:28,064
あなたを正式に逮捕します。ボス！私を置いていかないで！
You are officially arrested. Wait! Boss! Boss! You can't leave me, boss!

740
00:44:28,064 --> 00:44:35,064
またね、敗者さん！バイバイ！
See you later, loser! Bye!

741
00:44:35,064 --> 00:44:43,064
追いかけるわよ！乗って！私、運転できない！
We're going to catch her! Get in! Let's catch her! I can't drive!

742
00:44:43,064 --> 00:44:54,064
私たち二人きりだね、ベイビー。
It's just you and me, baby.

743
00:45:14,372 --> 00:45:16,172
All right, the place is empty.

744
00:45:16,572 --> 00:45:19,372
Got about ten minutes before the guard's next patrol.

745
00:45:29,872 --> 00:45:32,772
So, this is the YAGOO trophy...

746
00:45:32,972 --> 00:45:36,572
the Giga-Mega National Treasure.

747
00:45:39,172 --> 00:45:42,572
I'm gonna make a fortune on this!

748
00:45:51,672 --> 00:45:54,672
This is Justice. Is this an emergency?

749
00:45:55,272 --> 00:45:57,272
Help! Help! Please! Please!

750
00:45:57,372 --> 00:46:00,272
Please, is anybody here right now?

751
00:46:00,272 --> 00:46:02,172
I don't know what to do, please!

752
00:46:02,172 --> 00:46:05,172
Calm down and take a deep breath.

753
00:46:05,172 --> 00:46:08,072
Can you tell me exactly what happened?

754
00:46:40,072 --> 00:46:44,272
Uh, calm down... Calm down.

755
00:46:57,272 --> 00:46:59,872
Leave it to us. Leave it to us.

756
00:46:59,872 --> 00:47:03,572
Justice is on the way right now!

757
00:47:05,172 --> 00:47:07,472
Everyone, we have a case.

758
00:47:07,672 --> 00:47:10,572
The ultimate national treasure has been stolen.

759
00:47:10,572 --> 00:47:13,072
Head to the scene immediately!

760
00:47:13,472 --> 00:47:15,972
The ultimate national treasure?

761
00:47:16,572 --> 00:47:19,372
You mean the YAGOO statue?

762
00:47:19,572 --> 00:47:22,572
Who even wants that? Just let them keep it.

763
00:47:26,172 --> 00:47:29,072
Gigi, that is disrespectful!

764
00:47:29,072 --> 00:47:33,272
It is still the ultimate national treasure.

765
00:47:34,272 --> 00:47:36,572
We're counting on you.

766
00:47:39,172 --> 00:47:42,072
Fine, I'm on it.

767
00:47:46,172 --> 00:47:49,072
Oh, wait, Liz!

768
00:47:49,172 --> 00:47:54,672
The super limited edition sweetie pizza drops in just three minutes!

769
00:47:56,072 --> 00:47:58,072
It's limited quantity, okay?

770
00:47:58,272 --> 00:48:01,472
That means I absolutely have to buy it!

771
00:48:01,872 --> 00:48:04,572
Okay, so only two minutes left now.

772
00:48:05,172 --> 00:48:06,872
Just go already!

773
00:48:07,072 --> 00:48:12,872
No! Oh, mio dio! The portal is loading! No! No!

774
00:48:16,872 --> 00:48:19,572
Cecilia, did you get any information?

775
00:48:33,472 --> 00:48:37,072
Cecilia!

776
00:48:38,072 --> 00:48:39,272
Hold on!

777
00:48:39,372 --> 00:48:42,572
Who the hell changed my keyboard to American?!

778
00:48:49,272 --> 00:48:51,872
But I love your keyboard, Ceci!

779
00:48:52,172 --> 00:48:53,672
This was you?!

780
00:48:53,672 --> 00:48:56,572
You... You absolute garbage can!

781
00:48:56,672 --> 00:48:59,072
When I get to you, I'm going to...

782
00:49:01,072 --> 00:49:04,872
Cecilia, every second counts here.

783
00:49:05,172 --> 00:49:08,572
I know, I know. All right, found a backdoor in the telescope.

784
00:49:08,572 --> 00:49:10,872
Cracking the encrypted protocol via brute force.

785
00:49:10,872 --> 00:49:13,872
Enforcing the security patch overdrive on the mainframe system security data...

786
00:49:13,872 --> 00:49:15,572
In English, please.

787
00:49:15,572 --> 00:49:18,072
Fine. I'm in.

788
00:49:18,172 --> 00:49:22,572
The suspect is a woman dressed entirely in black.

789
00:49:22,672 --> 00:49:26,572
Height looks around 168 centimeters.

790
00:49:26,672 --> 00:49:30,072
She really likes people wearing helmets.

791
00:49:30,272 --> 00:49:33,872
Ah, she's fleeing north. If you move now, you can still catch her.

792
00:49:34,072 --> 00:49:38,272
You all heard her. Let's move out and apprehend the suspect!

793
00:49:38,272 --> 00:49:41,072
For justice!

794
00:50:00,080 --> 00:50:03,480
Raora, what are you doing? You're not even driving! Do you know how to drive a car?

795
00:50:03,480 --> 00:50:05,180
Put your foot on... on the gas pedal!

796
00:50:05,180 --> 00:50:07,580
Wait! Wait, wait, wait, wait! What?

797
00:50:07,580 --> 00:50:10,080
There's a horse in front of us!

798
00:50:10,080 --> 00:50:11,880
There's no freaking horse. What freaking horse?

799
00:50:11,880 --> 00:50:14,380
Oh my god, there's a freaking horse. Oh, the horse is right there. Oh my god.

800
00:50:17,480 --> 00:50:19,480
Is this for real? No way that's a real horse!

801
00:50:19,480 --> 00:50:23,580
Oh, we must get out of here now!

802
00:50:24,080 --> 00:50:28,080
Wait, Gigi! I'm not gonna be able to eat my limited-edition San Martin!

803
00:50:28,080 --> 00:50:31,280
My pizza's gonna get cold!

804
00:50:31,280 --> 00:50:33,280
Wait, wait, wait, wait!

805
00:50:33,280 --> 00:50:36,080
Horses like cucumbers, right? I think there's a cucumber in the trunk.

806
00:50:36,080 --> 00:50:38,080
What? A cucumber? In the trunk?

807
00:50:38,080 --> 00:50:40,580
Gigi! Why do you have a cucumber in your pockets right now?

808
00:50:40,580 --> 00:50:45,880
Gigi, you know I hate cucumbers!

809
00:50:45,880 --> 00:50:47,380
You know why? What?

810
00:50:47,380 --> 00:50:52,580
Gigi, you know I hate cucumbers! Why do you have cucumbers right now?!

811
00:50:52,580 --> 00:50:56,580
Ew! Get out of here!

812
00:50:56,580 --> 00:50:58,580
You know where I'm gonna put the cucumber? Where?

813
00:50:58,580 --> 00:51:03,880
Get out of here right now! I don't want to see that cucumber! Ew!

814
00:51:03,880 --> 00:51:07,480
What about the horse? What about for the horse? No! What about for the horse?

815
00:51:07,480 --> 00:51:11,880
Oh, you hate me. Don't you freaking hate me? You hate me! So you hate me! So you hate me! Just say it! Tell me!

816
00:51:11,880 --> 00:51:18,580
You know how I feel! Why did you bring cucumbers? You brought cucumbers, and you know that I hate- and I hate cucumbers! I hate the taste, I hate everything about cucumbers!

817
00:51:18,580 --> 00:51:24,580
We talked about that many times! Stop, stop, stop laughing!

818
00:51:26,580 --> 00:51:29,880
Those two are away with the fairies.

819
00:51:29,880 --> 00:51:35,080
Cecilia! Do you have any updates on the suspect's location?

820
00:51:35,080 --> 00:51:38,080
Mmh, almost there...

821
00:51:39,880 --> 00:51:41,280
Cecilia?

822
00:51:41,280 --> 00:51:43,080
A little bit more...

823
00:51:43,080 --> 00:51:45,580
Cecilia...

824
00:51:46,580 --> 00:51:49,080
Cecilia Immergreen!

825
00:51:49,080 --> 00:51:51,080
No! I missed!

826
00:51:51,080 --> 00:51:54,080
Look what you did, Liz! You ruined my perfect score!

827
00:51:54,080 --> 00:51:56,580
I was so close!

828
00:51:56,580 --> 00:51:59,880
Not you too!

829
00:52:02,080 --> 00:52:05,580
Did I fail them as a mother?

830
00:52:05,580 --> 00:52:08,580
My heart breaks as their big sister.

831
00:52:08,580 --> 00:52:14,280
I've done everything in my power to look after those three.

832
00:52:14,280 --> 00:52:20,580
Those three wild, eccentric little sisters...

833
00:52:20,580 --> 00:52:23,580
