834
00:52:23,580 --> 00:52:27,580
I gave them my all!

835
00:52:27,580 --> 00:52:34,080
Oh, what did I do to deserve such cruelty?

836
00:52:34,080 --> 00:52:37,580
Where did I go wrong?

837
00:52:37,580 --> 00:52:46,080
Where did my guidance stray away from the path?!

838
00:52:50,080 --> 00:52:54,580
You... you guys were still... still there, huh?

839
00:52:54,580 --> 00:52:57,080
We're sorry, ERB.

840
00:52:57,080 --> 00:53:00,080
I promise I will be a good girl.

841
00:53:00,080 --> 00:53:04,280
Big sister! Big sister! Big sister!

842
00:53:04,280 --> 00:53:08,080
It's just allergies. I'm not crying. You're crying.

843
00:53:08,080 --> 00:53:14,880
Thank you! We love you, big sister!

844
00:53:14,880 --> 00:53:19,580
Happy ever after!

845
00:53:19,580 --> 00:53:21,880
Justice just like that! Justice did get them.

846
00:53:22,580 --> 00:53:24,580
Guys, everyone!

847
00:53:24,580 --> 00:53:28,080
It's the thief who stole the ultimate yogurt statue!

848
00:53:28,080 --> 00:53:30,080
We're gonna kill them.

849
00:53:30,080 --> 00:53:32,080
